---
layout: base
---
<section class="intro">
  <p>
    I'm a PhD candidate at Stanford, advised by <a href="{{ site.advisor }}">Dan Yamins</a>. I work on
    <strong>world models</strong> and <strong>3D scene understanding</strong> — scalable autoregressive
    transformers for perception, controllable generation, and multimodal reasoning over spatiotemporal
    data. This is where I write about research and half-formed ideas.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="posts">
  <h2 class="section-title">Writing</h2>
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="post-item">
      <div class="post-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }} · {{ post.templateContent | readingTime }} min read</div>
      <h3 class="post-item-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
      {% if post.data.description %}<p class="excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<p class="prev-note">
  My older site lives at
  <a href="{{ site.oldsite }}">sites.google.com/view/wanheelee</a>.
</p>
